            <section class="section">
                <h2>Overview</h2>
                <p>This comprehensive guide provides detailed instructions for submitting mortgage lead data to VMG's Lead Management System via secure HTTP POST requests. The API enables real-time lead transfer with immediate validation and response handling.</p>
            </section>
            
