            <section class="section">
                <h2>Implementation Guidelines</h2>
                <div class="notes-grid">
                    <div class="note-card">
                        <h4>Implementation Notes</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Call API immediately after warm transfer completion</li>
                            <li>Include comprehensive error handling</li>
                            <li>Format phone numbers as 10 digits without special characters</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="note-card">
                        <h4>Best Practices</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Post lead data within 5 seconds of call transfer</li>
                            <li>Validate all required fields before submission</li>
                            <li>Store API tokens securely and rotate regularly</li>
                            <li>Monitor success/failure rates for all submissions</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
